{"id":"int-8155548ba9ca2b385f36974b5e79378e","kind":"field_change","created_at":"2026-06-16T16:42:02.163567Z","actor":"dmshvetsov","issue_id":"risk-trading-nx7","extra":{"field":"status","new_value":"closed","old_value":"deferred","reason":"Rejected Balance-backed Long quantity. Long.quantity is an option claim amount, while sui::balance::Balance<T> represents real coin supply/resource accounting. Using Balance for Long would imply coin/token supply semantics or collateral custody on the Long object, which conflicts with the current design where BaseCoin/QuoteCoin collateral stays in the Series CollateralPool. Keep Long.quantity as u64 unless Longs are intentionally redesigned as separate fungible Sui assets."}}
